  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Add
    A FieldTransformer for an add operation.
    AddSequenceElement
    A FieldTransformer for adding a SequenceElement.
    Clear
    A FieldTransformer for clear operations.
    FieldAddSequenceElementTransformerFactory
    A factory for field transformers that add sequence elements.
    FieldAddTransformerFactory
    A factory for add field transformers.
    FieldClearTransformerFactory
    A factory for clear field transformers.
    FieldRemoveTransformerFactory
    A factory for remove field transformers.
    FieldReplaceTransformerFactory
    A factory for replace field transformers.
    FieldTransformer
    A field transformer, which models the influence of a statement of a single field.
    FieldTransformerFactory
    An abstract factory for field transformers.
    FieldTransformerManager
    A manager singleton for field transformers, which is the entry point for generating field transformers.
    FieldTransformerUtils
    Utility functions for field transformers.
    IdentityFieldTransformer
    The identity field transformer, which does not modify anything.
    Remove
    A field transformer for remove operations;
    Replace
    A field transformer for replace operations.
    TopFieldTransformer
    A top field transformer, which maps any FieldValue to an unknown value.
